<![CDATA[<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</span><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">As a member of the NCS Regional Youth Board for North London, we have an exclusive opportunity just for you...</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000" size="5">Take part in the National NCS Sales Celebration Event 2016!</font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;">We're looking for 2-3 members to speak at the event and help our NCS Sales team understand exactly what it's like for a young person taking part in the programme. The details of the event are as follows:</div><div style="text-align: left;"><ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial"><b style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Date: </b>Monday 23rd May</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b><font color="#cc0000">Time: </font></b>13:00 - 16:30</font></li><li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial"><b style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Location: </b>Venue in Angel, Islington (exact location confirmed upon application)</font></li><li><b style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Your role: </b>We'll need you to walk our team through your experience of NCS, leading activities to help staff understand the programme from your perspective as well as how to make sure future NCS participants are fully supported in their journey.</li></ul><div>If you are interested in taking part, please contact&nbsp;<b><font color="#cc0000">samuel.hepher@the-challenge.org</font></b>. As the event takes place on a weekday, we can provide you with a proof of absence letter to give to your school if necessary.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">In the meantime, keep an eye out for information on your next NCS Regional Youth Board meeting!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Kind regards,</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div><b><font color="#cc0000">The Challenge Society</font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></div>]]></td>
